Ndaye Mulamba, "djogo" ya lisano ya ndembo, mosani monene ya Leopards, equipe nationale ya RDC akufi na Afrique du Sud, elobi ministre ya Sports Papy Niango Iziamay. 
 Mosani ya Congo liye ayebanaki mpe na kombo ya "Mutumbula", azalaki bobele mosani moko atikalaka kotiya mingete 9 na phase finale moko ya coupe dâ€™Afrique des nations, na 1974 ntango RDC (Zaire) elongaki competition liye mpo na mbla ya mibale.
Ndaye akufi na mibu 70, azalaki attaquant ya AS Vita Club. Alongaki mpe na equipe na ye Vita Club coupe africaine des clubs champions na 1973.
Abetaki mpe na Renaissance ya Kasai mpe na As Bantous.
Ndaye akufi na Afrique du Sud esika wapi azalaki na lopitalo.
Azuwaki medaille ya ordre nationale des Leopards mpe medaille ya merite ya Centenaire ya Fifa.